comments.body:
原来项目中jira verify token成功后的拿到response的API调用过程

[https://chief-spleen-3f7.notion.site/ADM-360-0c21aa0ee2d44285b6f2752e13b65306|https://chief-spleen-3f7.notion.site/ADM-360-0c21aa0ee2d44285b6f2752e13b65306|smart-link]
原来代码中verify token时会call三个接口去enrich column和users的信息，这里先只对column config接口返回的数据进行处理，剩下的信息拆成单独的卡做。

Jira api: GET [https://dorametrics.atlassian.net/rest/agile/1.0/board/2/configuration|https://dorametrics.atlassian.net/rest/agile/1.0/board/2/configuration]

(Basic Auth)

api: 

GET [http://localhost:4322/api/v1/boards/jira|http://localhost:4322/api/v1/boards/jira]

request body : {
    "boardName": "",
    "boardId":"2",
    "email":"",
    "projectKey":"ADM",
    "site":"dorametrics",
    "token":""
}
